				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>How terribly depressing and lovely.<br />
The second person really drew me in and made me sad and grumpy.</p>
<p>I dug &#8220;meaningless muddle of useless things.&#8221;<br />
Very much &#8220;Stuff. Whatever.&#8221;<br />
You&#8217;ve painted the (grey!) picture of the shop and Our Hero really well.<br />
I could also go for a little de-adverbiation, but didn&#8217;t find it too distracting.</p>
<p>Great take(s) on the theme!</p>
